files.Title: AIModule
files.Summary: A module for use with an ArtificialIntelligence.

files.Title: ARKillRect
files.Summary: A rectangle that kills any creature that enters it.

files.Title: AirBreatherCreature
files.Summary: A creature that can drown underwater.

files.Title: ArtificialIntelligence
files.Summary: Base class for a realized creature AI.

files.Title: BodyChunk
files.Summary: A circular hitbox with a radius and a mass.

files.Title: EntityID
files.Summary: An ID used in generating variations in creatures.

files.Title: Ghost
files.Summary: An instance of an Echo.

files.Title: IDrawable
files.Summary: Room objects with IDrawable will be added to the drawableObjects list and will be drawn as long as the room is visible. Mostly used for objects that you want full control over how their drawn.

files.Title: Moth
files.Summary: A realized BigMoth or SmallMoth.

files.Title: PhysicalObject
files.Summary: A room entity that has collision.

files.Title: PlacedObject
files.Summary: An object thats placed using DevTools and gets loaded when the room gets loaded.

files.Title: Player
files.Summary: A realized Slugcat (or Slugpup) player or NPC.

files.Title: RainWorld
files.Summary: The singleton MonoBehavior holding most of the game.

files.Title: StaticWorld
files.Summary: A helper class that initializes and contains every CreatureTemplate in the game.

files.Title: UpdatableAndDeletable
files.Summary: A basic room entity that exists inside a room. This entity can be updated and deleted in the room hense the name.

files.Title: VoidSea.PlayerGhosts.Ghost
files.Summary: A single voidsea player ghost that follows the movements of the player with a slight deviation in swim speed.

files.Title: VoidSea.PlayerGhosts
files.Summary: Controls the numerous copies of the player you see at the bottom of the void sea.
